Package: amr.surveillance
Title: Global AMR Surveillance Monthly Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Analyst", "Team", email = "analytics@example.gov.uk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extracts antimicrobial resistance isolate records from BigQuery,
    calculates monthly resistance rates by organism and country, and writes
    a 12-month surveillance summary back to the analytics dataset.
    Tracks five key organisms across five countries for public health reporting.
    This is a worked example for the 'R to the Cloud' guide.
